<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Founders | Aquiplex</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Meet the founders of Aquiplex – the minds behind Aqua AI and Aqua Project Engine.">

  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: auto;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 42px);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #6366f1);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    }

    .hero p {
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: clamp(15px, 3vw, 18px);
    }

    /* ── Founders grid ── */
    .founders-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #1e293b;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 25px;
      transition: 0.3s;
      border: 1px solid #334155;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      border-color: #6366f1;
    }

    .name {
      font-size: clamp(18px, 4vw, 22px);
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .role {
      color: #38bdf8;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .desc {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #cbd5f5;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .links {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .links a {
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #0f172a;
      background: #38bdf8;
      padding: 9px 14px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: 0.2s;
      min-width: 100px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .links a:hover {
      background: #6366f1;
      color: white;
    }

    /* ── Vision ── */
    .vision {
      margin-top: 80px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 10px;
    }

    .vision h2 {
      font-size: clamp(22px, 5vw, 28px);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .vision p {
      color: #94a3b8;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: auto;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* ── Explore section ── */
    .section {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 60px;
      padding: 0 10px;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: clamp(20px, 4vw, 26px);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .cta-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 8px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #6366f1);
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 15px;
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
    }

    .cta-btn:hover {
      opacity: 0.85;
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 60px;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #475569;
      border-top: 1px solid #1e293b;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    /* ── Mobile ── */
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .container {
        padding: 30px 16px;
      }

      .founders-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .card {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .links a {
        flex: 1;
      }

      .section .cta-btn {
        display: block;
        margin: 8px auto;
        max-width: 260px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <%- include("every") %>

  <div class="container">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="hero">
      <h1>Meet the Founders</h1>
      <p>The visionaries building Aquiplex and shaping the future of AI-driven creation.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- FOUNDERS -->
    <div class="founders-grid">

      <!-- Founder 1 -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="name">Chhanda Prabal Das</div>
        <div class="role">Co-Founder & Advisor</div>
        <div class="desc">
          The original mind behind Aquiplex, Chhanda Prabal Das is a student and entrepreneur
          who has worked on multiple early-stage startups including Uniqence and Acodet.
          <br><br>
          His experience in building products from scratch shaped the vision of Aquiplex—
          an ecosystem focused on execution, not just ideas.
        </div>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/chhanda.pr" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/chhanda-prabal-das-7198a0280" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Founder 2 -->
      <div class="card">
        <div class="name">Ananya Prabal Das</div>
        <div class="role">Chief Executive Officer (CEO)</div>
        <div class="desc">
          Leading the execution of Aquiplex, Ananya Prabal Das manages daily operations
          and ensures consistent development of the platform.
          <br><br>
          He plays a key role in turning ideas into real features, working closely with
          the product vision to build and scale Aquiplex efficiently.
        </div>
        <div class="links">
          <a href="https://www.instagram.com/ananya.p.r.a" target="_blank">Instagram</a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ananya-prabal-das-024293383" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- VISION -->
    <div class="vision">
      <h2>Our Vision</h2>
      <p>
        Aquiplex is being built as a complete AI ecosystem where users can generate content,
        build projects, and turn ideas into reality using advanced AI systems like Aqua AI
        and the Aqua Project Engine.
        <br><br>
        This is just the beginning.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Explore Aquiplex</h2>
    <a href="/about" class="cta-btn">About Platform →</a>
    <a href="/aqua-ai" class="cta-btn">Aqua AI →</a>
    <a href="/aqua-project-engine" class="cta-btn">Project Engine →</a>
  </div>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> AQUIPLEX. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
